<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_591" id="294v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_591_r1l13">Hanſen Hawt cʒu Ottelſtorff </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_591_r1l14">Vnſer dinſt beuor . <expan>Han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> hawt . Als Jr vns <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>geſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> h </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_591_r1l15">vnd begert habt euch für vns vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>ern</ex></expan> cʒeſichern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_591_r1l16"><expan>hıecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd mittfaſten ſchierſt etc . das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_591_r1l17">wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> . Vnd alſo ſüllt Jr vor vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_591_r1l18"><expan>hıecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd des Suntags Letare cʒu Mitfaſten ſchıerſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_591_r1l19">ſicher ſein on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . Vnd wenn Jr in <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒeit her gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_591_r1l20"><expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> kumt So ſüllt Jr . Vnd ewr freunde die mit euch her </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_591_r1l21">kumen cʒu Vnd von vns für vns vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / vnd bey vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_591_r1l22">für <expan>allermeniklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> drey tag geleẏte <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . Alſdann <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_591_r1l23">vvir ewr rede hören / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>do<ex>min</ex>icam</expan> Jnuocauit / Anno xxııȷ<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_591" id="294v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hansen Hawt czu Ottelstorff </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Unser dinst bevor. <expan>Han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Hawt, als ir uns
                                <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ges<ex>chriben</ex></expan> und begert habt, euch für uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>ern</ex></expan> cze sichern
                        <expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <app><note><q type="date">mittfasten schierst</q>14.03.1423</note></app> etc.,
                        das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>, und also süllt ir vor uns und
                        den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und des <app><note><q type="date">suntags letare czu mitfasten
                            schierst</q>14.03.1423</note></app> sicher sein on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Und wenn ir in
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czeit her gen
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> kumt, so süllt ir und ewr freunde,
                        die mit euch her kumen czu und von uns für uns und die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und bey uns für
                                <expan>allermeniklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> drey tag geleyte
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; alsdann
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr rede hören.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>icam</expan> invocavit anno xxiii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.
                    </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
